@startuml
title Diagramme de deploiement - E-Services (logique conteneurs)

skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8

actor "Navigateur" as Nav

node "Machine hote" as Host {
  node "Docker" as Docker {
    artifact "e-services-web\n<<image>>\nReact + Nginx" as Web
    artifact "e-services-api\n<<image>>\nLaravel PHP" as Api
    database "PostgreSQL\n<<conteneur>>" as Db
    storage "volume fichiers\npieces jointes" as VolData
    storage "volume donnees\nPostgreSQL" as VolPg
  }
}

Nav --> Web : HTTPS\n(cookies Secure)

Web --> Api : proxy /api\nHTTP reseau interne

Api --> Db : JDBC\nport 5432 interne

Api --> VolData : montage volume\nfichiers utilisateur

VolPg .. Db : persistance SQL

note bottom of Docker
  Communication : reseau docker bridge entre conteneurs.
  Ports HTTP ou HTTPS exposes sur la machine hote.
  Secrets via variables environnement (non commites).
end note

@enduml
